    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dungeon Sweeper is a tactical roguelike that fuses classic Minesweeper-style tile clearing with auto-battler combat. Each dungeon is a dangerous puzzle - every step could trigger a battle with a hidden monster, or reward you with loot and progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282820/extras/477496ee9b3c5a90d8598fe4585b3c6c.poster.avif?t=1755063858\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282820/extras/477496ee9b3c5a90d8598fe4585b3c6c.webm?t=1755063858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282820/extras/477496ee9b3c5a90d8598fe4585b3c6c.mp4?t=1755063858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open tiles to uncover numbered clues and flag suspected monster positions. If you guess wrong - or choose to risk it - you’ll enter an strategic battle where your hero’s gear, stats, and items determine the outcome. Victory brings rewards, defeat ends your run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282820/extras/b193fe3d37d27212ebe2a9ffd18140ed.poster.avif?t=1755063858\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282820/extras/b193fe3d37d27212ebe2a9ffd18140ed.webm?t=1755063858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282820/extras/b193fe3d37d27212ebe2a9ffd18140ed.mp4?t=1755063858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each playthrough offers randomized dungeons, increasing difficulty, and new loot combinations to discover. The deeper you go, the more intense the encounters become.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're a fan of minesweeper puzzles or tactical roguelikes, Dungeon Sweeper offers a fresh challenge that rewards observation, risk-taking, and smart decisions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧨 Minesweeper-inspired exploration with hidden enemies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ Fast-paced auto-battler combat when monsters are triggered</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🛡️ Loot and equip gear to build your hero across the run</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌀 Procedurally generated dungeons with escalating difficulty</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >☠️ Permadeath and replayability at the core</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you master the tiles and survive the depths of the dungeon?</p>",
